title: Coinbase Q3 earnings breakdown + Startup Checklist: Crafting a brand & knowing your market | E1323
description: First, Jason breaks down Coinbase's Q3 earnings and takes a look at the broader trends in crypto trading (01:13). Then, Jason runs through 10 points of his "Startup Checklist" focused on crafting a brand & knowing your market (11:25). At the end, Jason answers a question from the live audience (43:16).
